div.div:
The connections between these simple iterations of functions can identify similar/different interface queries like equivalent queries and optimal queries.
The result of the iterations of these functions is the same structure (a linear connection) but that can be another graph variable (alternatives like 'a common variable of the problem/solution'), and similarly an iteration that results in a useful simplifying iteration like a 'useful general connection/filter/change' is another alternative.
